text: Maysky () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Maysky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 356 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 57 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Maysky, Republic of Bashkortostan
